        "subject": "LU-19654 tests: increase SHUTDOWN_ATTEMPTS to 5",
        "message": "LU-19654 tests: increase SHUTDOWN_ATTEMPTS to 5\n\nWhile running failover tests with FAILURE_MODE=HARD,\nsometimes the test node was not powered off after\nattempting 3 times. This patch increase the attempts\nto try to avoid the failures.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial \\\n  env=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,FAILURE_MODE=HARD \\\n  clientcount=4 mdtcount=1 mdscount=2 osscount=2 \\\n  austeroptions=-R failover=true iscsi=1 \\\n  clientdistro=el8.10 serverdistro=el8.10 \\\n  fstype=ldiskfs testgroup=failover-part-2\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial \\\n  env=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,FAILURE_MODE=HARD \\\n  clientcount=4 mdtcount=1 mdscount=2 osscount=2 \\\n  austeroptions=-R failover=true iscsi=1 \\\n  clientdistro=el9.6 serverdistro=el9.6 \\\n  fstype=zfs testgroup=failover-part-2\n\nChange-Id: I806af787205e7628de22373103e6381e046531d4\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62857\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Yang Sheng <ys@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
